or folk har en tendens til \u00e5 bli st\u00e5ende p\u00e5 samme sted av gammel vane. Spesielt n\u00e5r skuret st\u00e5r der fortsatt. Det kan i grunnen skje selv om vi har f\u00e5tt p\u00e5 plass skilt om flytting ogs\u00e5, sier Nissen."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|trondheim"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "9835035a363acc3271d344343c23a6437b06f5db1fea42a2d8e8448cef7b09c0"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-01-24T13:06:55.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "I g\u00e5r ble drosjeholdeplassen i Nordre gate flyttet til Dronningens gate. Likevel stiller folk seg fortsatt p\u00e5 den \u00abgamle\u00bb holdeplassen i Nordre gate."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1194691.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/stians-taxikart"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/2226799cb0c05a365219a83efe220780f89f2e48.jpg?597cd515"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Full forvirring rundt drosjeholdeplass -adressa.no", "Skal hindre br\u00e5k", "Setter opp infoskilt"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "2226799cb0c05a365219a83efe220780f89f2e48"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "trondheim"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "home-and-garden"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["informere publikum", "holdeplass", "flytte", "gate", "kort varsel"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["nordre", "dronningens", "norgestaxi", "tr\u00f8ndertaxi", "munkegata"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": "trondheim"}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value"